ecensioni/" >Opera</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/roberto-campanella/" title="View all posts by Roberto Campanella" rel="author">Roberto Campanella</a></span> </span> <span class="meta-tags" title="Tags"> <i class="icon-tags"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/allopera-da-rossini-a-verdi/" rel="tag">All'opera da Rossini a Verdi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/carmela-remigio/" rel="tag">Carmela Remigio</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/claudio-marino-moretti/" rel="tag">Claudio Marino Moretti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/igor-stravinskij/" rel="tag">Igor Stravinskij</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/juan-francisco-gatell/" rel="tag">Juan Francisco Gatell</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marcello-nardis/" rel="tag">Marcello Nardis</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/matteo-ferrara/" rel="tag">Matteo Ferrara</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/michael-leibundgut/" rel="tag">Michael Leibundgut</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/natasha-petrinsky/" rel="tag">Natasha Petrinsky</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/silvia-regazzo/" rel="tag">silvia regazzo</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-la-fenice-di-venezia/" rel="tag">Teatro La Fenice di Venezia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/the-rakes-progress/" rel="tag">The Rake's progress</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="All'opera da Rossini a Verdi, Carmela Remigio, Claudio Marino Moretti, Igor Stravinskij, Juan Francisco Gatell, Marcello Nardis, Matteo Ferrara, Michael Leibundgut, Natasha Petrinsky, Opera lirica, silvia regazzo, Teatro La Fenice di Venezia, The Rake's progress"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/8906e5c97475cd1b0aec5e7449ba59a4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Roberto-Campanella-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Roberto Campanella" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Roberto Campanella"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/roberto-campanella/">View all articles by Roberto Campanella</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/07/intervista-al-baritono-renato-bruson/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Intervista al baritono Renato Bruson</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/07/verona-arena-opera-festival-2014turandot/" rel="next">Verona, Arena Opera Festival 2014:&#8221;Turandot&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2014/07/the-rakes-progress-al-teatro-la-fenice-di-venezia/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="